          "description": "Really happy to have started with this dentist. I've had a cleaning, a crown put on a cracked tooth, a root canal with crown on another tooth, and I'm getting a night guard--and the whole experience has been excellent from Dr Corey Brick's very skilled care, to the hygienist, to the assistant for the more involved dental work, to the front desk. All both professional and kind--better front to back than I've encountered with any other dental office. Highly recommend.",
