          "description": "I'm always in a rush bec of work, and they didn't make me wait at all.  Everything was so clean and beautiful and the staff super helpful and quick to respond.  The Dr. Fixed my front tooth where everyone else had told me I have to shave it down more before fixing or put veneers which I won't do.  It looks perfect. Unbelievable. He's so knowledgeable and nice. Have been looking for an honest dentist like this for about 10 years.",
