          "description": "Amazing first visit! Everyone was incredibly friendly, and Dr. Brick was thorough, knowledgeable, and very gentle. The experience felt nostalgic, in the best way, reminding me of how dental appointments used to feel. You\u2019re truly not treated like just another patient here.\n\nIt\u2019s clear that the team genuinely cares and takes the time to work with you toward your goals. I left feeling excited about my future treatments and confident, with a clear plan for my upcoming visits.\n\nThank you so much!",
