          "description": "I hadn't gone to the dentist in 7 years, partially because of life circumstances as well as a general fear of clinical settings and they treated me so kindly here. They began the exam right on time, no wait! They checked in on me often and played calming things on the tv during the cleaning. I have had 2 hygienists and both women have been great. Dr. St Laurent is great too. Even the receptionists are quite kind to me. I recommend this spot to all my coworkers.",
